{
  "stem": "21310.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I have read in some book that, that the Germans forbade any composers except for Jewish composers, which I didn't even know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because all I know is that I, I fell in love with Mozart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I met-- about a year ago, I met a man who had survived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a musician in, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a violinist-- a pianist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I ask him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, do you remember, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he apparently played in, in that symphony.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said, I can't understand why they were saying that only-- no German composer, that only Jewish composers would be played.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the official line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we would put these ad-- not ads, but announcements-- Mendelssohn, always Mendelssohn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they-- once you were in, they played whatever they wanted to play.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But officially, it was always Mendelssohn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then there were these clandestine courses organized for children-- for young people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Classes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, classes, because there were so many [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] teachers that found themselves, and high school teachers and even professors, university professors.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they organized these clandestine courses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I attended one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were about six girls-- five, six girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would meet with a different teacher every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, you know, have a lot of homework.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, I got a very good education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was taught Latin by somebody, by a known classicists.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was taught physics and calculus by a-- from a astronomer, a older man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember him sitting-- he had-- you know, in the winter, we only had this one little [NON-ENGLISH], little lamp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the only source of heat and, and light.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
